data.description: Welcome to your new home at 1000 S Western St, where classic charm and modern convenience harmonize perfectly. This lovely 2-story, 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom corner-lot house boasts a beautiful brick exterior that catches the eye. Inside, an open floor plan seamlessly connects spacious living areas for both daily life and entertaining. Located in a sought-after neighborhood, this property offers easy access to schools, shopping, dining, and major highways, making it an ideal place to call home. Don't miss this opportunity to make 1000 S Western St your new address for comfort and style.
